      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUNGRY HOGARTH (6) scored last start by 4 metres at Mildura over 1790m after an encouraging minor placing the start before. Meeting a deeper field this time but he is up to the challenge. EYESEALITTLE (8) settled handy then went to the lead and boxed on well to finish second in a 1700m race at Horsham last start, beaten 6 metres at her first run back from a layoff. Drawn to enjoy an economical run and might sweat on the sprint lane. Needs to be at her best to beat this field but she good enough to play a major role. KEAYANG HUNGRY (7) is the next best after finishing runner-up over 1700m at Horsham last time out. ISTHISTHEREALLIFE (2) did not make an impact last start but strips fitter third-up and can improve from this favourable draw.",
